    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Super-C Constellation\nSuper Constellation\n60-passenger Constellation\nSilver Falcon\nThe World's Most Advanced Airliners\nEAL P 200",
      "EASTERN AIR LINES",
      "EASTERN'S MEALS are pre-\npared by private caterers, selected\non the basis of long\nsuccessful\nexperience, the excellence of their\nchefs, and dependability.\nBecause individual tastes are so\ndifferent, items on the menu are\nselected for their broadest possi-\nble appeal. Our primary purpose\nis to please you.\nWe appreciate the pleasure of\nserving you and hope to have you\nwith us again, often!\nMenu\nShrimp Cocktail • Sauce Rouge\nCrisp Saltines\nBroiled Filet Mignon with Mushroom Caps\nBaked Stuffed Potato Au Gratin\nFrench Cut String Beans\nHearts of Lettuce Salad • French Dressing\nDinner Roll • Creamery Butter\nChocolate Nut Sundae\nCoffee • Tea • Milk"
    ],
